description.en:
The AXEL.Network isn’t coming, it’s here. It’s live. A fully operational Masternode network bringing the future of the distributed web.

We’ve built our Content Distribution Network (CDN) from the ground up using distributed technologies to foster a movement from centralized systems to a decentralized world. It’s a network that will change how the internet handles data and bring quick and free private file-sharing to anyone, anywhere!

The future is decentralized. The future is AXEL.

⭐Take a look at some of the exciting things that took place at AXEL in the month of April⭐

Highlights include:

✅AXEL announces partnerships with the Florida and Mississippi Bar Associations

✅Google and Apple login integration for Axel Go

✅Business plans now available for Axel Go users

✅Update on the blockchain upgrade, steps for MN holders

and more......

Be sure to bookmark our updates page and check back each month. 👉 https://get.axel.org/monthly-update 👀

AXEL Announces Partnership with Florida Bar Association

Read all about it here:

https://www.prweb.com/releases/axel_announces_partnership_with_florida_bar_association_and_launch_of_axel_go_apps_new_business_tier_subscription_designed_for_the_legal_industry/prweb17868750.htm

⭐News, notes and highlights from an exciting February at Axel!⭐

Highlights include:

✅AXEL hosted a (sold out) CLE webinar for the Nevada Bar Association

✅Android version 1.2.7.1 of AXEL Go launched with new features

✅AXEL named in Masternode.buzz's "Top Performing Masternode" list in 2 different weeks

✅A MAJOR upgrade to the network and blockchain

and more......

Be sure to bookmark our updates page and check back each month. 👉 https://get.axel.org/monthly-update 👀

⭐Take a look at some of the exciting things that took place at AXEL in the month of December⭐

Highlights include:

✅AXEL receives a US Patent for its blockchain technology

✅In app walkthrough added to AXEL Go

✅AXEL named in Masternode.buzz's Week 50 list of Best Performing Masternodes 

✅UI Improvements to the AXEL Go Web Wallet 

and more......

Be sure to bookmark our updates page and check back each month. 👉 https://get.axel.org/monthly-update 👀

🙌 AXEL Pushes Toward the Future of Innovation: Receives Latest Patent for its Blockchain Technology 🥳

AXEL, creators of the AXEL Network, a globally distributed and decentralized content delivery network, has been awarded a new patent by the United States Patent and Trademark Office (USPTO) for its proprietary blockchain technology. 🙏

https://www.prweb.com/releases/axel_pushes_toward_the_future_of_innovation_receives_latest_patent_for_its_blockchain_technology/prweb17583492.htm 👀

✅ MobileAppDaily names AXEL Go their App of the Week

and more......
